    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Companion Appearance Enhancement</span>. This biomechanical remnant is a constant reminder of the many and diverse forms that existence can take.<br><br>Earn the trust of wild animals to adopt companions. Interact with companions to customise their appearance.",
